name: Maharashtra Steel
overview:
Established in the year 2004, we, “Maharashtra Steel Fabrication”, are one of the trusted organizations engaged in manufacturing and supplying a supreme quality range of Slotted Angles & Panel Accessories, Storage Racks and Industrial Pipes & Furniture.

Our Team: Engineers Quality controllers Metal experts R&D experts Warehousing experts Logistics personnel

Infrastructure: We have a sophisticated infrastructure, which is well-managed by a team of highly experienced professionals. The entire infrastructure is segregated into different departments like designing, production, quality testing, R&D, warehousing and others.

Quality Assurance: Our organisation aims at offering a superior quality range of Slotted Angles & Panel Accessories, Storage Racks and Industrial Pipes & Furniture to the customers. These products are manufactured using genuine quality raw material procured from some of the most trusted vendors of the industry.

Client Satisfaction: Our organisation is widely appreciated in the market for offering genuine quality Slotted Angles & Panel Accessories, Storage Racks and Industrial Pipes & Furniture to the customers. These products are designed and made as per the exact details provided by the clients.

Our Products: File Slotted Angle Racks Slotted Angles & Panel Accessories Metal Racks & Almirah Storage Cupboards Industrial Pipes Office Chairs MS Galvanised Sheet
